headline: TMUS Expands Reach in Fiber-to-the-Home Market With Lumos Buyout
summary: The joint venture of T-Mobile and EQT acquire Lumos to accelerate the deployment of fiber-to-the-home Internet access across the country.

headline: T-Mobile US (NasdaqGS:TMUS) Partners With NYMobile For Personalized 5G Phone Numbers
summary: T-Mobile US (NasdaqGS:TMUS) experienced a notable price increase of 22% over the last quarter, possibly influenced by several key developments. The expansion of NYMobile's services, utilizing T-Mobile's 5G network, combined with personalized phone number offerings, captured significant attention. Partnerships with Thales and SIMPL IoT strengthened T-Mobile's IoT market presence, while a deal with NVIDIA aimed at developing AI-powered networks demonstrated a commitment to future innovation...
